description:
At the height of her fame, CSI: Miami star Eva LaRue received a handwritten letter signed “Freddie Krueger.” Her life was never the same. What followed was a 12-year nightmare filled with grotesque threats, violent fantasies, and a faceless stalker who hunted her and her daughter.

The new P+ Original documentary My Nightmare Stalker: The Eva LaRue Story premieres November 13, exclusively on Paramount+.
